{"id":144,"parent_id":141,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":144,"title":"1 Corinthians 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","Milk comes before meat in the Church—Men’s works will be tried by fire—The Saints are the temple of God, and if they are faithful, they will inherit all things."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.1","order":"03.09.003.16936"},["b","1"],"And I, brethren, could not speak unto you as unto spiritual, but as unto carnal,",["i","even"],"as unto babes in Christ."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.2","order":"03.09.003.16937"},["b","2"],"I have fed you with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"milk"],", and not with meat: for hitherto ye were not able",["i","to bear it,"],"neither yet now are ye able."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.3","order":"03.09.003.16938"},["b","3"],"For ye are yet",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"carnal"],": for whereas",["i","there is"],"among you",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"envying"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"strife"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"divisions"],", are ye not carnal, and walk as men?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.4","order":"03.09.003.16939"},["b","4"],"For while one saith, I am of Paul; and another, I",["i","am"],"of Apollos; are ye not carnal?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.5","order":"03.09.003.16940"},["b","5"],"Who then is Paul, and who",["i","is"],"Apollos, but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"ministers"],"by whom ye believed, even as the Lord gave to every man?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.6","order":"03.09.003.16941"},["b","6"],"I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"planted"],", Apollos watered; but God",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"gave"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"increase"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.7","order":"03.09.003.16942"},["b","7"],"So then neither is he that planteth any thing, neither he that watereth; but God that giveth the increase."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.8","order":"03.09.003.16943"},["b","8"],"Now he that planteth and he that watereth are one: and every man shall receive his own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"reward"],"according to his own labour."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.9","order":"03.09.003.16944"},["b","9"],"For we are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"labourers"],"together with God: ye are God’s",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"husbandry"],",",["i","ye are"],"God’s building."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.10","order":"03.09.003.16945"},["b","10"],"According to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"grace"],"of God which is given unto me, as a wise masterbuilder, I have laid the foundation, and another buildeth thereon. But let every man take heed how he buildeth thereupon."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.11","order":"03.09.003.16946"},["b","11"],"For other",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"foundation"],"can no man lay than that is laid, which is Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.12","order":"03.09.003.16947"},["b","12"],"Now if any man build upon this foundation gold, silver, precious stones, wood, hay, stubble;"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.13","order":"03.09.003.16948"},["b","13"],"Every man’s work shall be made manifest: for the day shall declare it, because it shall be revealed by fire; and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"fire"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"try"],"every man’s work of what sort it is."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.14","order":"03.09.003.16949"},["b","14"],"If any man’s work abide which he hath built thereupon, he shall receive a reward."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.15","order":"03.09.003.16950"},["b","15"],"If any man’s work shall be burned, he shall suffer loss: but he himself",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"shall"],"be saved; yet so as by fire."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.16","order":"03.09.003.16951"},["b","16"],"Know ye not that ye are the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"temple"],"of God, and",["i","that"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Spirit"],"of God dwelleth",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"in"],"you?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.17","order":"03.09.003.16952"},["b","17"],"If any man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"defile"],"the temple of God, him shall God destroy; for the temple of God is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"holy"],", which",["i","temple"],"ye are."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.18","order":"03.09.003.16953"},["b","18"],"Let no man deceive himself. If any man among you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"seemeth"],"to be wise in this world, let him become a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"fool"],", that he may be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"wise"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.19","order":"03.09.003.16954"},["b","19"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"wisdom"],"of this",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"world"],"is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"foolishness"],"with God. For it is written, He taketh the wise in their own",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"craftiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.20","order":"03.09.003.16955"},["b","20"],"And again, The Lord",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"knoweth"],"the thoughts of the wise, that they are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"vain"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.21","order":"03.09.003.16956"},["b","21"],"Therefore let no man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"glory"],"in men. For all things are yours;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.22","order":"03.09.003.16957"},["b","22"],"Whether",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Paul"],", or Apollos, or Cephas, or the world, or life, or death, or things present, or things to come;",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"all"],"are yours;"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.23","order":"03.09.003.16958"},["b","23"],"And ye are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"Christ’s"],"; and Christ",["i","is"],"God’s."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.2a","order":"03.09.003.16959"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/5.12.11-14"},"Heb. 5:12 (11–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/2.2.1-3"},"1 Pet. 2:2 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.22"},"D&C 19:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.40"},"50:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.3a","order":"03.09.003.16961"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/carnal-mind"},"TG Carnal Mind"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"},"Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.3b","order":"03.09.003.16963"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/envy"},"TG Envy"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.3c","order":"03.09.003.16965"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.3d","order":"03.09.003.16967"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.5a","order":"03.09.003.16969"},["b","5a"],["span.small","GR"],"servants.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.6"},"2 Cor. 3:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.6a","order":"03.09.003.16971"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/4.37.36-38"},"John 4:37 (36–38)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.1"},"1 Cor. 9:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.6b","order":"03.09.003.16973"},["b","6b"],["span.small","GR"],"caused, gave growth."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.6c","order":"03.09.003.16975"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.27.26-29"},"Mark 4:27 (26–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.8a","order":"03.09.003.16977"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reward"},"TG Reward"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wages"},"Wages"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.9a","order":"03.09.003.16979"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/6.1"},"2 Cor. 6:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.9b","order":"03.09.003.16981"},["b","9b"],["span.small","GR"],"cultivated field, farm."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.10a","order":"03.09.003.16983"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.11a","order":"03.09.003.16985"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.18"},"Matt. 16:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.30"},"2 Ne. 4:30"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cornerstone"},"TG Cornerstone"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.13a","order":"03.09.003.16987"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2.2-3"},"Mal. 3:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.13b","order":"03.09.003.16989"},["b","13b"],["span.small","GR"],"test, put to proof.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.15a","order":"03.09.003.16991"},["b","15a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Cor. 3:15 …",["i","may"],"…"],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.1